{"title":"Kalshi wins","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/904299470/0/marginalrevolution~Kalshi-wins.html","date":1725888470000,"content":"<p>From an announcement, slightly edited by me:</p>\r\n<blockquote><p>Kalshi has defeated the CFTC, legalizing election markets in the US for the first time in 100 years.  After years of battling with the US government, we won in court: <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://nam11.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Fregulation%2Fare-you-ready-to-bet-on-u-s-elections-a-judges-ruling-opens-the-door-556abc73&amp;data=05%7C02%7Ctcowen%40gmu.edu%7C601ea3d7b435463d13e608dcd080f056%7C9e857255df574c47a0c00546460380cb%7C0%7C0%7C638614500653873836%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJWIjoiMC4wLjAwMDAiLCJQIjoiV2luMzIiLCJBTiI6Ik1haWwiLCJXVCI6Mn0%3D%7C60000%7C%7C%7C&amp;sdata=VeoQrTr960l066j6Z8sRxj8iMk6dwLdsUXGOFUiF9UI%3D&amp;reserved=0\" target=\"_blank\"><u>the District Court of Columbia just ruled in our favor</u></a>, legalizing trading on U.S. elections and overthrowing a long-time ban that has been standing since the Great Depression.</p></blockquote>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/09/kalshi-wins.html\">Kalshi wins</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/904299470/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/904299470/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/904299470/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/904299470/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\